Sentencas: Ba1-xPrxCo1-yFeyO3-delta (BPCF) perovskite oxides have been synthesized and investigated as cathode materials for low temperature solid oxide fuel cells (LT-SOFCs).
Titulo: Ba1-xPrxCo1-yFeyO3-δ as cathode materials for low temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Compared with those of Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.8Fe0.2O3-delta (BSCF) and Sm0.5Sr0.5CoO3 (SSCo) cathode materials.
Titulo: Ba1-xPrxCo1-yFeyO3-δ as cathode materials for low temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: BPCF has a lower polarization resistance at decreased temperatures.
Titulo: Ba1-xPrxCo1-yFeyO3-δ as cathode materials for low temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: In particular, Ba0.5Pr0.5Co0.8Fe0.2O3-delta showed the lowest polarization loss among the different compositions as a cathode material for LT-SOFCs.
Titulo: Ba1-xPrxCo1-yFeyO3-δ as cathode materials for low temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The area specific resistance (ASR) of Ba0.5Pr0.5Co0.8Fe0.2O3-delta as a cathode material is 0.70 and 0.185 Omega cm(2) at 500 degrees C and 550 degrees C, respectively.
Titulo: Ba1-xPrxCo1-yFeyO3-δ as cathode materials for low temperature solid oxide fuel cells
